{"tid":1607490,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【黑色10.1】《蘋果日報》今日隨報附送「兄弟爬山」海報","createTime":"2019-10-01T00:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T01:05:18.000Z","uid":279895,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"98fb3458e2d31d471ac078f785ca1cf4d9763dc6","tid":1607490,"uid":279895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T00:36:38.000Z","msg":"大家買溪錢賀佢老母之外，記得買返份蘋果呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zRk0QU4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzRk0QU4.png&h=679360f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，齊上齊落，我們一個都不能少！反送中運動以來，不少民間創作振奮士氣，也慰藉了受挫心靈。「harcourtromancist」創作的《兄弟爬山》畫作更特別深受逆權運動支持者的喜愛，《蘋果日報》徵得作者同意，今日隨報附送此畫作的跨頁海報，為香港打氣。<br />\n<br />\nharcourtromancist曾在instagram這樣說：「香港人，寧化飛灰、不作浮塵，光復香港、時代革命」。就算多艱難，今天一起走下去。香港人，加油！"},{"pid":"80ba60821a9f4b11172887ff766b8c23fe146dd3","tid":1607490,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T00:37:59.000Z","msg":"即刻去買！！"},{"pid":"8f8365be01890b9f0ed512ced8115c17607bc2c8","tid":1607490,"uid":77542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T00:40:40.000Z","msg":"靚"},{"pid":"3089191430112e44c7e49836b357dd58203917c8","tid":1607490,"uid":14244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T00:43:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3058b613f402be727423b6f962771fe267b1724c","tid":1607490,"uid":197086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T00:44:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6cc70d3faebf8ff487054d19253465352489c9ce","tid":1607490,"uid":289191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T00:44:58.000Z","msg":"蘋果揀啱了"},{"pid":"fc9d773667